    Brand & Logo Design Packages

    Differentiate your business with brand and logo design, including a full suite of uniquely branded assets most brands need to get started.

    Stand out from the competition with dynamic brand design

    All brand design services are custom and tailored to your business.

    Logo Design

    This includes a logo with all variations, including your primary logo, any secondary logos, custom marks, and/or brand icons.

    Visual Identity

    Custom color palettes, typography, visuals guide, and other elements that define the look and feel of your brand.

    Brand Style Guide

    Helpful document outlining brand standards, including logo, colors, type hierarchies, and other notes, to help keep the visuals of your brand consistent and on-brand.

    Print Marketing Assets

    Printed items like business cards, brand stationery, sales materials, packaging, signage or other physical materials.

    Digital Marketing Assets

    Items to help with digital marketing, including social media banners and posts, email marketing templates, online advertisements, sales pdfs, lead generation magnets, and other digital items.

    Brand Imagery

    Product photos, illustrations, stock photography, iconography, and other visual elements to help with brand recognition

    How it works

    01

    Brief & Strategy

    We start with a custom questionnaire to learn about your business, target market, and goals to guide the visual direction of the brand.

    02

    Design

    We land on a design direction through a moodboard, and design all the brand elements, including digital and printed materials

    03

    Handoff & Walkthrough

    As the final step, we deliver all the brand files, including logos, imagery, materials, and the brand guide, and show you how to use your new brand guide.

    Typically 2-4 weeks, depending on the package. E-commerce projects that involve product photography can take longer. The base package can take as little as 2 weeks. And most fall somewhere in the middle.
    At the beginning of the project, we will set you up with a dedicated project board that will outline the timeline and outstanding tasks. The board allows for commenting and submitting feedback and is a great way to stay on the same page about everything that's happening with your project.
    We design and develop in stages, and at each stage, you will be able to send your edits and feedback. The process is reiterative and because of it, there's an unlimited amount of edits you can request.
